definitions.definition: A person who makes , dispenses or sells lenses , spectacles .
A person trained and skilled in examining and testing the eyes for defects, in order to prescribe corrective lenses or treatment; an optometrist .

main_definition: A person who makes , dispenses or sells lenses , spectacles .
secondary_definitions: ( UK ) A person trained and skilled in examining and testing the eyes for defects, in order to prescribe corrective lenses or treatment; an optometrist .
